title: Snaps - Top 5 Games: Are Dabo Swinney & Clemson on upset alert? Mississippi St-Alabama, UCLA-Oregon
itunes:title: Snaps - Top 5 Games: Are Dabo Swinney & Clemson on upset alert? Mississippi St-Alabama, UCLA-Oregon
description:
Aaron Murray and T-Bob Hebert break down the Top 5 games of Week 8 of the college football season. Are Dabo Swinney and Clemson or Nick Saban and Alabama on upset alert at home against Syracuse and Mississippi State? Will UCLA continue it's magical season on the road against Oregon? And how will Texas and TCU stay hot against Oklahoma State and Kansas State? #Volume #ColinCowherd #Herd
